# Local (uncommitted) development config for Flutter --dart-define-from-file
#
# IMPORTANT:
# - On web, the Google Maps API key is NOT a secret (it ships to the browser).
# - Protect it with HTTP referrer restrictions in Google Cloud Console.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your key.
MAPS_API_KEY=YOUR_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY
